WEBVTT

00:00.075 --> 00:01.668
Previously on "Midnight, Texas"...

00:01.702 --> 00:03.420
The veil between the living and the dead

00:03.435 --> 00:05.226
- is awful thin here.
- I think you're gonna

00:05.250 --> 00:07.132
lead an army and seal the veil forever.

00:07.148 --> 00:09.384
It's your destiny. I got a vision.

00:09.407 --> 00:12.468
Midnight in flames
and you in the center,

00:12.515 --> 00:14.299
the only one to stop it.

00:14.315 --> 00:15.482
You need to go back.

00:15.518 --> 00:17.972
If I don't, they all die?

00:18.007 --> 00:19.323
You came back.

00:19.335 --> 00:21.034
You and I, we've got
unfinished business.

00:21.077 --> 00:22.534
I'm here because of her.

00:22.581 --> 00:24.579
I don't want to be turned.

00:24.613 --> 00:26.394
Once you turn, you'll like it.

00:27.616 --> 00:29.527
Olivia, I'm so...

00:29.543 --> 00:30.699
Back off!

00:30.730 --> 00:31.980
Despite what happened,

00:32.021 --> 00:33.021
I love you.

00:33.055 --> 00:35.023
As soon as Fiji's safe,

00:35.057 --> 00:36.491
I'm leaving Midnight.

00:36.525 --> 00:37.738
Fiji...

00:37.770 --> 00:40.028
Colconnar, he's chosen you.

00:40.069 --> 00:41.895
There's no way in hell
I'm letting this thing

00:41.931 --> 00:44.165
get anywhere near you, I promise, Fij.

00:44.200 --> 00:46.567
I'm a virgin witch, a
powerful virgin witch,

00:46.613 --> 00:48.261
and that is why it wants me.

00:48.295 --> 00:49.528
Your emotions...

00:51.282 --> 00:53.249
- You need to control them.
- Jeremy?

00:53.277 --> 00:56.111
Colconnar sent me because
he knew you'd listen to me.

00:56.145 --> 00:59.047
Go to him willingly, or they all die.

