01:33.983 --> 01:36.618
We know where they're taking her.

01:36.652 --> 01:39.087
Going back to Midnight,
bringing her to Colconnar.

01:39.121 --> 01:40.989
To use her.

01:41.023 --> 01:43.152
When the demons came
through the veil last time,

01:43.191 --> 01:45.665
they used women to
go forth and multiply.

01:45.696 --> 01:47.228
That thing wants to...

01:47.263 --> 01:49.264
It wants to have sex with her.

01:49.298 --> 01:50.665
Which is utterly awful.

01:50.699 --> 01:52.267
But not surprising.

01:52.301 --> 01:54.766
Fiji's as powerful a natural
witch as I've ever seen.

01:54.807 --> 01:56.574
All the more powerful
because she hasn't...

01:56.610 --> 01:58.239
Yes, we know. She's a virgin.

01:58.274 --> 01:59.773
I don't give a damn why it wants her.

01:59.775 --> 02:01.959
It's not gonna lay a finger or a claw

02:01.990 --> 02:03.733
or whatever the hell it has on her.

02:03.764 --> 02:05.580
We won't let it.

02:16.824 --> 02:18.291
What has he done?

02:18.325 --> 02:21.060
You can feel him, can't you?

02:24.198 --> 02:25.798
Getting closer,

02:25.833 --> 02:27.300
stronger.

02:32.206 --> 02:33.840
- Oh, God, is that it?
- Not yet.

02:33.874 --> 02:35.308
He will come to you tonight.

02:35.342 --> 02:37.844
Fiji...

02:37.878 --> 02:41.280
Colconnar is very eager to meet you.

02:43.817 --> 02:45.451
When I died,

02:45.486 --> 02:47.857
the shaman said the
first demon was gonna rise

02:47.889 --> 02:51.121
on the night of a blood
moon, that's tonight.

02:51.168 --> 02:53.143
Well, besides the creepy
name, what does that mean?

02:53.145 --> 02:54.894
Xylda and I wouldn't even do readings

02:54.928 --> 02:56.462
on nights of blood moons.

02:56.497 --> 02:58.464
They create a potent psychic environment

02:58.499 --> 03:00.333
that can be a conduit for evil.

03:00.367 --> 03:01.567
It's too dangerous.

03:01.602 --> 03:03.236
It's also a full moon.

03:03.270 --> 03:04.804
This just keeps getting better.

03:04.838 --> 03:06.339
Fiji's spell worked.

03:06.373 --> 03:07.974
I know how to kill Colconnar.

03:10.911 --> 03:13.012
Oh, God.

03:13.047 --> 03:15.415
Colconnar sent them to guard you.

03:15.449 --> 03:17.884
Creek, Olivia, Bobo,

03:17.918 --> 03:19.819
you guys find Fiji.

03:19.853 --> 03:21.832
Keep her safe until Colconnar's gone.

03:21.871 --> 03:23.256
Done.

03:23.290 --> 03:24.566
How are you gonna kill it?

03:24.598 --> 03:26.387
- Details aren't important.
- Aren't they?

03:26.434 --> 03:28.835
Before we worry about killing Colconnar,

03:28.871 --> 03:31.067
what are we gonna do about the wraiths?

03:31.098 --> 03:32.365
They barely touched me...

03:32.399 --> 03:34.534
burned right through my
clothes, hurt like hell.

03:34.568 --> 03:37.270
What kind of weapons did we bring?

03:37.304 --> 03:40.440
This is everything.

03:40.474 --> 03:43.042
Wraiths are spirit
manifestations of evil.

03:43.077 --> 03:45.344
An ax isn't gonna cut it.

03:45.379 --> 03:47.380
I'm thinking we go old school.

03:47.414 --> 03:49.449
They're evil.

03:49.477 --> 03:51.180
Evil doesn't like holy water.

03:51.214 --> 03:52.766
It burns, they recoil.

03:52.805 --> 03:54.583
We clear a path to Fiji.

03:54.618 --> 03:55.718
Will this do?

03:55.752 --> 03:57.586
Yeah, I can sanctify this

03:57.621 --> 03:59.322
and bless these weapons.

03:59.361 --> 04:01.423
While they're with Fiji,
we head to the pawn shop.

04:01.425 --> 04:04.693
Why the pawn shop?

04:04.728 --> 04:06.695
There's stuff there I need.

04:13.737 --> 04:14.823
Hey.

04:17.908 --> 04:19.478
Are you gonna be okay

04:19.502 --> 04:22.311
using consecrated weapons?

04:22.345 --> 04:25.214
Over the years, I've developed
a tolerance for holy water.

04:25.248 --> 04:26.976
At most, it stings.

04:27.013 --> 04:28.617
Wow, I hate to break it to you,

04:28.644 --> 04:30.312
but you're just not that evil.

04:32.789 --> 04:34.390
It can't be easy for you,

04:34.424 --> 04:36.659
knowing what Colconnar intends for Fiji.

04:36.693 --> 04:39.403
Nothing's going to happen to her.

04:39.447 --> 04:41.514
You look tired.

04:41.536 --> 04:43.273
You need energy?

04:43.294 --> 04:46.302
Or do you need to not be scared?

04:46.336 --> 04:48.671
Maybe.

04:48.705 --> 04:50.840
But we're not together anymore, so...

04:50.874 --> 04:53.809
probably not the best idea.

04:53.844 --> 04:55.678
There's something you're not telling me.

04:55.712 --> 04:58.447
How exactly are you
planning to kill Colconnar?

04:58.482 --> 04:59.915
- Details aren't...
- Important?

04:59.950 --> 05:01.917
You said that.

05:01.952 --> 05:03.686
You're trying to spare me, aren't you?

05:03.720 --> 05:04.854
Look, we're gonna do this,

05:04.888 --> 05:06.255
whatever the risks are.

05:06.289 --> 05:07.990
So, yeah, I'm trying to spare you.

05:08.024 --> 05:09.570
And I'd appreciate it if you let me.

05:09.585 --> 05:11.427
Fine. Spare me.

05:11.461 --> 05:13.179
But don't die this time.

05:13.221 --> 05:14.221
Deal.

05:17.434 --> 05:19.898
It's time you prepare
yourself for his arrival.

05:19.932 --> 05:23.435
You look... unworthy.

05:23.477 --> 05:25.278
Jeremy, Jeremy, Jeremy, Jeremy...

05:25.304 --> 05:26.871
If there's any part of you

05:26.914 --> 05:30.016
in there, your heart, your kindness,

05:30.034 --> 05:31.601
please don't let him do this to me.

05:31.629 --> 05:33.861
There is no part of me that's Jeremy.

05:40.023 --> 05:41.857
You're one of them.

05:41.892 --> 05:44.693
Colconnar was in my head...

05:46.090 --> 05:48.495
In my sleep, in my dreams.

05:48.532 --> 05:51.700
It's how Colconnar knows you.

05:51.735 --> 05:52.968
Which means...

05:54.504 --> 05:55.971
We all know you.

05:58.601 --> 06:00.335
We're a reminder.

06:00.353 --> 06:02.688
You're not all that
different from Colconnar.

06:02.730 --> 06:05.766
Your powers destroy. They kill.

06:05.789 --> 06:08.817
Just like his.

06:08.852 --> 06:11.487
It's time you got ready for him.

06:28.905 --> 06:32.374
Don't cry...

06:32.409 --> 06:34.923
Fiji.

06:34.963 --> 06:36.731
He's right.

06:40.417 --> 06:44.086
I have to get ready.

07:01.104 --> 07:03.564
Okay, we save Fiji,

07:03.603 --> 07:04.603
kill a demon,

07:04.630 --> 07:06.731
close a portal to hell.

07:06.760 --> 07:09.545
And we don't die. Sound like a plan?

07:09.579 --> 07:12.481
My flesh is burning. Stop talking.

07:12.515 --> 07:13.916
Let's go.

